1515
01:11:07,805 --> 01:11:08,973
Wow.

1516
01:11:10,391 --> 01:11:11,434
Wow.

1517
01:11:12,018 --> 01:11:13,311
It's actually quite...

1518
01:11:14,312 --> 01:11:15,313
bad.

