- (Sighs)
- Dessert requires a large barrel

1540
01:13:08,801 --> 01:13:10,481
that is supposed to be
there in the corner.

1541
01:13:11,095 --> 01:13:12,722
(Chuckles softly) Do you see a barrel?

1542
