01:13:35,161 --> 01:13:36,245
Right, Margot?

1552
01:13:37,330 --> 01:13:38,497
- Margot: Yes.
- Yes, what?

1553
01:13:39,790 --> 01:13:41,417
Yes, chef.

1554
