1562
01:14:09,779 --> 01:14:11,072
(Bird squawks)

1563
01:14:24,919 --> 01:14:26,671
(Richard breathing heavily)

1564
01:14:28,881 --> 01:14:31,425
(Dramatic music intensifies)

1565
01:14:35,930 --> 01:14:37,306
Excuse me. Uh...

1566
01:14:37,390 --> 01:14:38,516
(Dramatic music fades)

